Award-winning rapper Kwesta has disappointed fans by letting them know that July marks the end for his club performing career. Kwesta went on social media to announce that his ditching club performances. Taking to social media the Khethile Khethile hit-maker wrote “Ending my club gig career this July...” Fans can forget about watching him perform live at clubs as the rapper will strictly be performing at larger events and concerts. Its been a few months since the star tied the knot and he evidently making some lifestyle changes. READ: WATCH: KWESTA’S WHITE WEDDING The news has been received well, while some fans are not happy with Kwesta's latest announcement.         